						               													<description>A long time ago, the British Empire colonized the world and propagated the consumption of tea. The british forces were eventually repelled by a small country in the Far East. And so, tea was banned as it had grown to become a symbol of the british imperialism in many countries. However, people who couldn't resist the allure of tea secretly had tea brought to their homes by mafia organizations and held tea parties. The mafia members in charge of delivering tea were dressed in maid uniforms. They became known as &amp;quot;Maid Mafia.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Maid x Mafia x Kai is the second game in the serie after the first Maid x Gun x Tea which was a smaller scale prototype.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battle on the map of Kobe with your fellow players. First player to reach 25 points on the score track win the game. Gain points by smuggling tea in a pick-up and delivery gameplay and bringing them from the ports/warehouses to the shop that will serve it. Hire additional maids that will share their movement points to deliver more tea and battle henchmen or other player's maid with the use of the confrontation card system.&amp;#10;But be careful, you are all part of the same organization so attacking another player will brand you as an enemy. Yet, among the many actions at your disposal, it may sometimes be the best option. Happy smuggling!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
